cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation systems. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes an alternative approach to the current state-of-the-art machine translation systems. Additionally, the use of convolutional neural networks suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as well. The paper also involves the use of attention-like properties, which could make it relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
